# Extension Rules

## Storage
- Use chrome.storage.local for all persistence — never localStorage
- Buffer tab events locally, flush every 5 min via alarm
- Max buffer size: 500 events — flush immediately if exceeded

## Security
- Strip query strings before storing any URL
- Never capture chrome://, extension://, or localhost pages
- Respect the user's sensitive domain exclusion list
- CSP: script-src 'self' only

## API Calls
- Always use src/utils/api-client.js — never raw fetch
- api-client.js handles auth headers and token refresh automatically
